	    </div>
	    
	    <div class="sectionDescription">
	       
            <p>
	           The various dialogKit objects accept callback arguments. These callbacks should be methods or functions that accept a <i>sender</i> argument. The dialogKit object, when clicked, typed in, etc. will call the callback and pass itself as the sender.
